.SH LIBBSON
.sp
A Cross Platform BSON Library for C
.SS Introduction
.sp
libbson builds, parses, and iterates \fI\%BSON\fP documents, the native data format of MongoDB. It also converts BSON to and from JSON, and provides a platform compatibility layer for \fI\%the MongoDB C Driver\fP\&.
.SS Installing libbson
.sp
The following guide will step you through the process of downloading, building, and installing the current release of libbson.
.SS Supported Platforms
.sp
The MongoDB C Driver is \fI\%continuously tested\fP on variety of platforms including:
